TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {22062=LAKEWOOD — It’s a problem that has reared its ugly head time and again for Dakota Ridge. Three times this season the Eagles — against Green Mountain, Denver South and now Wheat Ridge — have had their 4A Plains Conference rivals on the ropes. And three times they’ve let them off.
